name: Chinese zodiac series (goat)
description:
People with the Goat zodiac sign were born in 1943, 1955, 1967, 1979, 1991, 2003, 2015 and 2027.
In the Chinese zodiac, the goat has positive, creative, and imaginative energy. In addition, the figure of the goat zodiac is also full of affection and courtesy.
